  "solution": {
    "text": "<p>maximumscore 2<br>voorbeeld van een antwoord:<br>De fotonenergie moet groter zijn dan de bandgap. (Dus halfgeleiders met een bandgap kleiner dan <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn> <mo>,</mo> <mn>75</mn> <mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">eV</mi>&#160;</mrow></math>zijn geschikt / halfgeleiders met een bandgap groter dan <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn> <mo>,</mo> <mn>10</mn> <mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">eV</mi>&#160;</mrow></math>zijn niet geschikt.)</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid;border-bottom-width:1px;border-left-style:!important;border-left-width:!important;border-right-style:!important;border-right-width:!important;border-top-style:solid;border-top-width:1px;text-align:center;width:auto;\">halfgeleider</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-style:solid !important;border-top-width:1px !important;text-align:center;width:auto;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"bold-italic\">E</mi> <mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mtext>gap </mtext></mrow></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo> <mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi mathvariant=\"bold\">e</mi> <mi mathvariant=\"bold\">V</mi> </mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></math></td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-style:solid !important;border-top-width:1px !important;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-style:solid !important;border-top-width:1px !important;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td sty