style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">Si</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>3</mn> </mrow></msub><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mtext></mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">N</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>4</mn>&#160;</mrow></msub></math></td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\">5</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">ongeschikt</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\">GaAs</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\">1,43</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">geschikt</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-left-style:solid !important;border-left-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\">GaP</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;text-align:center;width:auto;\">2,26</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">geschikt</td><td style=\"border-bottom-style:solid !important;border-bottom-width:1px !important;border-right-style:solid !important;border-right-width:1px !important;border-top-color:!important;border-top-style:none;width:auto;\">&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ul><li>inzicht dat de bandgap niet groter mag zijn dan de fotonenergie<br>1</li><li>consequent invullen van de tabel<br>1</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>Opmerking</i><br><i>Als de kandidaat naast het argument dat de fotonenergie groter moet zijn dan de bandgap ook noemt dat de uitgezonden fotonen zichtbaar licht moeten zijn en dus naast <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">Si</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>3</mn> </mrow></msub><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mtext></mtext><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">N</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>4</mn>&#160;</mrow></msub></math>ook Si en GaAs als ongeschikt noteert, dit niet aanrekenen.</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
